!!!
%html{xmlns: "http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"}
  %head
    %meta{content: "width=device-width", name: "viewport"}/
    %meta{content: "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %title Offerchat
    %link{href: "https://s3.amazonaws.com/offerchat-emails/email.css", rel: "stylesheet", type: "text/css"}/
  %body{bgcolor: "#FFFFFF"}
    %table.head-wrap
      %tr
        %td
        %td.header
          .content
            %table
              %tr
                %td{align: "center"}
                  %a.logo{href: "https://www.offerchat.com"}
                    %img{alt: "Offerchat logo", src: "https://s3.amazonaws.com/offerchat-emails/logo.png"}/
        %td
    %table.body-wrap
      %tr
        %td
        %td.container{bgcolor: "#FFFFFF"}
          .content
            %table
              %tr
                %td
                  %h3 Hi #{@user.first_name},
                  %h4.lead Just dropping by to remind you that you have 1 day left before your Pro Trial expires.
                  %p
                    As we stated in our previous emails, you will have the option to upgrade to a paid plan of your choice and continue
                    to enjoy the best of what Offerchat has to offer now and in the future.
                  %p
                    Upgrade now to unlock these 2 features only available in our paid plans:
                    %br/
                    * Add multiple agents
                    %br/
                    * No Offerchat branding on your chat widget
                    %br/
                    * More exclusive features in every plan
                  %p.center
                    %a{ :href => "https://app.offerchat.com/#upgrade", :class => "btn" } Upgrade Now
                  %p
                    Drop me an email if you have any questions about upgrading!
                  %p Best Regards,
                  %p Vince
        %td
    .container.footer
      %p Â© 2014 Offerchat. All rights reserved.
      %p Unit 333, UP CebuInIT, Gorordo Avenue, Lahug, Cebu City, Philippines 6000

    = image_tag MIXPANEL.tracking_pixel("Opened One Day Remaining Email", { :distinct_id => @user.email })
